title: Rasheeda Liberty on Her Sports Agency, Fielding NFL Prospects
description: Rasheeda Liberty, founder and CEO of Lady Lib Sports & Entertainment, discusses Texas as a prime region for scouting future professional football players. She speaks with Katie Greifeld and Romaine Bostick on The Close. (Source: Bloomberg)
